#: admin/access.rst:110
msgid "`Review`"
msgstr "`Tinjauan`"

#: admin/access.rst:111
msgid "Approve translations in a review."
msgstr "Menyetujui terjemahan dalam tinjauan."

#: admin/access.rst:113
msgid "Available only if :ref:`review workflow <reviews>` is on."
msgstr "Hanya tersedia jika :ref:`tinjau alur kerja <reviews>` aktif."

#: admin/access.rst:115
msgid "For `Protected` and `Private` projects only:"
msgstr "Hanya untuk proyek `Dilindungi` dan `Privat`:"

#: admin/access.rst:117 snippets/roles.rst:156
msgid "`Translate`"
msgstr "`Terjemahkan`"

#: admin/access.rst:118
msgid "Translate the project and upload translations made offline."
msgstr "Terjemahkan proyek dan unggah terjemahan yang dibuat secara luring."

#: admin/access.rst:120
msgid "`Sources`"
msgstr "`Sumber`"

#: admin/access.rst:121
msgid ""
"Edit source strings (if allowed in the :ref:`project settings <component-"
"manage_units>`) and source-string info."
msgstr ""
"Sunting string sumber (jika diizinkan dalam :ref:`pengaturan proyek "
"<component-manage_units>`) dan info string sumber."

#: admin/access.rst:124
msgid "`Languages`"
msgstr "`Bahasa`"

#: admin/access.rst:125
msgid "Manage translated languages (add or remove translations)."
msgstr "Kelola bahasa yang diterjemahkan (tambahkan atau hapus terjemahan)."

#: admin/access.rst:127
msgid "`Glossary`"
msgstr "`Glosarium`"

#: admin/access.rst:128
msgid "Manage glossary (add, remove, and upload entries)."
msgstr "Kelola glosarium (tambahkan, hapus, dan unggah entri)."

#: admin/access.rst:130
msgid "`Memory`"
msgstr "`Memori`"

#: admin/access.rst:131
msgid "Manage translation memory."
msgstr "Kelola memori terjemahan."

#: admin/access.rst:133
msgid "`Screenshots`"
msgstr "`Tangkapan Layar`"

#: admin/access.rst:134
msgid "Manage screenshots (add, remove, and associate them to source strings)."
msgstr ""
"Kelola tangkapan layar (tambahkan, hapus, dan kaitkan ke string sumber)."

#: admin/access.rst:137 snippets/roles.rst:177
msgid "`Automatic translation`"
msgstr "`Terjemahan otomatis`"

#: admin/access.rst:138
msgid "Can use automatic translation."
msgstr "Dapat menggunakan terjemahan otomatis."

#: admin/access.rst:140
msgid "`VCS`"
msgstr "`VCS`"

#: admin/access.rst:141
msgid "Manage VCS and access the exported repository."
msgstr "Kelola VCS dan akses repositori yang diekspor."

#: admin/access.rst:143
msgid "`Billing`"
msgstr "`Tagihan`"

#: admin/access.rst:144
msgid "Access billing info and settings (see :ref:`billing`)."
msgstr "Akses info dan pengaturan tagihan (lihat :ref:`billing`)."

#: admin/access.rst:148
msgid ""
"These features are available on the :guilabel:`Access control` page in the "
"project’s menu :guilabel:`Operations` ↓ :guilabel:`Users`."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini tersedia di halaman :guilabel:`Kontrol akses` di menu "
"proyek :guilabel:`Operasi` ↓ :guilabel:`Pengguna`."

#: admin/access.rst:153
msgid ""
"You can limit teams to languages or components, and assign them designated "
"access roles (see :ref:`privileges`)."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membatasi tim pada bahasa atau komponen, dan memberi mereka peran "
"akses yang ditentukan (lihat :ref:`privileges`)."

#: admin/access.rst:159
msgid "Team administrators"
msgstr "Administrator tim"

#: admin/access.rst:163
msgid ""
"Each team can have team administrators, who can add and remove users within "
"the team."
msgstr ""
"Setiap tim dapat memiliki administrator tim, yang dapat menambah dan "
"menghapus pengguna dalam tim."

#: admin/access.rst:165
msgid "This is useful in case you want to build self-governed teams."
msgstr "Ini berguna jika Anda ingin membangun tim yang mengatur diri sendiri."

#: admin/access.rst:170
msgid "Inviting new users"
msgstr "Mengundang pengguna baru"

#: admin/access.rst:172
msgid ""
"Adding existing users will send them invitation to confirm. "
"With :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` the administrator can also invite new "
"users using e-mail. Invited users have to complete the registration process "
"to get access to the project."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan pengguna yang sudah ada akan mengirimkan undangan kepada mereka "
"untuk mengkonfirmasikan. Dengan :setting:`REGISTRATION_OPEN` administrator "
"juga dapat mengundang pengguna baru menggunakan surel. Pengguna yang "
"diundang harus menyelesaikan proses pendaftaran untuk mendapatkan akses ke "
"proyek."

#: admin/access.rst:177
msgid ""
"It is not required to have any site-wide privileges in order to do so, "
"access management permission on the project’s scope (e.g. a membership in "
"the `Administration` team) would be sufficient."
msgstr ""
"Tidak memerlukan hak akses di seluruh situs untuk melakukan hal tersebut, "
"izin pengelolaan akses pada cakupan proyek (mis. keanggotaan dalam tim "
"`Administrasi`) sudah cukup."

#: admin/access.rst:183
msgid ""
"If the invited user missed the validity of the invitation, a new invitation "
"has to be created."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengguna yang diundang melewatkan validitas undangan, undangan baru "
"harus dibuat."

#: admin/access.rst:186
msgid ""
"The same kind of invitations are available site-wide from "
"the :ref:`management interface <management-interface>` on "
"the :guilabel:`Users` tab. Both project administrators and site "
"administrators can also invite multiple users at once by pasting whitespace-"
"separated e-mail addresses. All invitations created in one bulk action use "
"the selected team, and site-wide bulk invites also apply the selected "
"superuser flag."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:193
msgid ""
"Site-wide user management is controlled by the global ``user.edit`` "
"permission. Unlike project access management, this is a trusted "
"administrative permission which allows editing user accounts across the "
"whole instance, including assigning site-wide teams and granting superuser "
"status to the managed account, even the caller's own account."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:199
msgid ""
"Bulk invitations are processed individually. Invalid addresses and addresses "
"with an already pending invitation are skipped while valid invitations are "
"still created and sent."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:205
msgid ""
"Weblate now does not automatically create accounts or add users to the "
"teams. This is only done after confirmation from the user."
msgstr ""
"Weblate kini tidak lagi membuat akun atau menambahkan pengguna ke tim secara "
"otomatis. Hal ini hanya dilakukan setelah ada konfirmasi dari pengguna."

#: admin/access.rst:211
msgid "Blocking users"
msgstr "Memblokir pengguna"

#: admin/access.rst:215
msgid ""
"If users misbehave in your project, you can block them from contributing. "
"With the relevant permissions blocked, users can still see the project, but "
"won't be able to contribute."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengguna berperilaku tidak semestinya dalam proyek Anda, Anda dapat "
"memblokir mereka agar tidak dapat berkontribusi. Dengan pemblokiran izin "
"yang relevan, pengguna tetap dapat melihat proyek, tetapi tidak dapat "
"berkontribusi."

#: admin/access.rst:222
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Translations contributions"
msgid "Cleaning up user contributions"
msgstr "Kontribusi terjemahan"

#: admin/access.rst:224
msgid ""
"When blocking spam or abusive accounts, project administrators can also "
"clean up the user's existing contributions in that project. "
"Use :guilabel:`Operations` ↓ :guilabel:`Users`, block the user, and select "
"the cleanup actions in the block form. For users who are already blocked, "
"use :guilabel:`Clean up user contributions` in the blocked users list."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:230
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "The options are:"
msgid "The available cleanup actions are:"
msgstr "Pilihannya adalah:"

#: admin/access.rst:232
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Revert user edits` reverts the latest editable translations by "
"the user."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:234
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reject user suggestions` rejects pending suggestions by the user."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:235
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete user comments` deletes comments by the user."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:237
msgid ""
"Site administrators with the site-wide ``user.edit`` permission can perform "
"the same bulk cleanup across all projects from the :ref:`management "
"interface <management-interface>` on the :guilabel:`Users` tab. Open the "
"user's profile, select the :guilabel:`Edit` tab, and "
"use :guilabel:`Contribution cleanup`."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:244
msgid "Per-project permission management"
msgstr "Pengelolaan izin per proyek"

#: admin/access.rst:246
msgid ""
"You can set your projects to :guilabel:`Protected` or :guilabel:`Private` "
"(see :ref:`acl`), and :ref:`manage users access <manage-acl>` per-project."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengatur proyek Anda ke :guilabel:`Dilindungi` "
"atau :guilabel:`Privat` (lihat :ref:`acl`), dan :ref:`kelola akses pengguna "
"<manage-acl>` per proyek."

#: admin/access.rst:249
msgid ""
"By default this prevents Weblate from granting access provided by `Users` "
"and `Viewers` :ref:`default teams <default-teams>` due to these teams’ own "
"configuration. This doesn’t prevent you from granting permissions to those "
"projects site-wide by altering default teams, creating a new one, or "
"creating additional custom settings for individual component as described "
"in :ref:`custom-acl` below."
msgstr ""
"Secara bawaan, hal ini mencegah Weblate memberikan akses yang diberikan oleh "
"`Pengguna` dan `Pengamat` :ref:`tim bawaan <default-teams>` karena "
"konfigurasi tim tersebut. Hal ini tidak mencegah Anda memberikan izin ke "
"proyek tersebut di seluruh situs dengan mengubah tim bawaan, membuat tim "
"baru, atau membuat pengaturan kustom tambahan untuk komponen individual "
"seperti yang dijelaskan dalam :ref:`custom-acl` di bawah."

#: admin/access.rst:255
msgid ""
"One of the main benefits of managing permissions through the Weblate user "
"interface is that you can delegate it to other users without giving them the "
"superuser privilege. In order to do so, add them to the `Administration` "
"team of the project."
msgstr ""
"Salah satu manfaat utama mengelola izin melalui antarmuka pengguna Weblate "
"adalah Anda dapat mendelegasikannya kepada pengguna lain tanpa memberi "
"mereka hak akses pengguna super. Untuk melakukannya, tambahkan mereka ke tim "
"`Administrasi` proyek."

#: admin/access.rst:260
msgid ""
"This project-scoped delegation is separate from the site-wide ``user.edit`` "
"permission. Membership in a project `Administration` team allows managing "
"access only for that project, while ``user.edit`` grants site-wide user "
"management in the Weblate UI and API and should be assigned only to fully "
"trusted site administrators."
msgstr ""

#: admin/access.rst:269
msgid "Per-project access tokens"
msgstr "Token akses per proyek"

#: admin/access.rst:273
msgid ""
"You can define project-scoped access tokens in :guilabel:`API access` tab. "
"The API tokens can have expiry date set, and their permissions can be "
"customized by team memberships same as with users."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menentukan token akses yang dicakup proyek di "
"tab :guilabel:`Akses API`. Token API dapat memiliki tanggal kedaluwarsa yang "
"diatur, dan izinnya dapat disesuaikan berdasarkan keanggotaan tim sama "
"seperti dengan pengguna."

#: admin/access.rst:285
msgid "Site-wide access control"
msgstr "Kontrol akses di seluruh situs"

#: admin/access.rst:289
msgid "This feature is unavailable on Hosted Weblate."
msgstr "Fitur ini tidak tersedia di Hosted Weblate."

#: admin/access.rst:291
msgid ""
"The permission system is based on roles defining a set of permissions, and "
"teams linking roles to users and translations, read :ref:`auth-model` for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"Sistem izin didasarkan pada peran yang mendefinisikan serangkaian izin, dan "
"tim yang menautkan peran ke pengguna dan terjemahan, baca :ref:`auth-model` "
"untuk rincian lebih lanjut."

#: admin/access.rst:295
msgid ""
"The most powerful features of the Weblate’s access control system can be "
"configured in the :ref:`management-interface`. You can use it to manage "
"permissions of any project. You don’t necessarily have to switch it "
"to :guilabel:`Custom` :ref:`access control <acl>` to utilize it. However you "
"must have superuser privileges in order to use it."
msgstr ""
"Fitur paling canggih dari sistem kontrol akses Weblate dapat "
"dikonfigurasikan dalam :ref:`management-interface`. Anda dapat "
"menggunakannya untuk mengelola izin proyek apa pun. Anda tidak perlu "
"mengalihkannya ke :guilabel:`Kustom` :ref:`kontrol akses <acl>` untuk "
"memanfaatkannya. Namun, Anda harus memiliki hak akses pengguna super untuk "
"menggunakannya."

#: admin/access.rst:301
msgid ""
"If you are not interested in details of implementation, and just want to "
"create a simple-enough configuration based on the defaults, or don’t have a "
"site-wide access to the whole Weblate installation (like on `Hosted Weblate "
"<https://hosted.weblate.org/>`_), please refer to the :ref:`manage-acl` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak tertarik dengan rincian implementasi, dan hanya ingin "
"membuat konfigurasi yang cukup sederhana berdasarkan pada pengaturan bawaan, "
"atau tidak memiliki akses ke seluruh pemasangan Weblate (seperti pada "
"`Hosted Weblate <https://hosted.weblate.org/>`_), silakan lihat "
"bagian :ref:`manage-acl`."

#: admin/access.rst:307
msgid "Site-wide permission management"
msgstr "Pengelolaan izin di seluruh situs"

#: admin/access.rst:309
msgid ""
"To manage permissions for a whole instance at once, add users to "
"appropriate :ref:`default teams <default-teams>`:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola izin untuk seluruh instansi sekaligus, tambahkan pengguna "
"ke :ref:`tim bawaan <default-teams>` yang sesuai:"

#: admin/access.rst:312
msgid ""
"`Users` (this is done by default by the :ref:`automatic team assignment "
"<autoteam>`)."
msgstr ""
"`Pengguna` (ini dilakukan secara bawaan oleh :ref:`penugasan tim otomatis "
"<autoteam>`)."

#: admin/access.rst:314
msgid ""
"`Reviewers` (if you are using :ref:`review workflow <reviews>` with "
"dedicated reviewers)."
msgstr ""
"`Peninjau` (jika Anda menggunakan :ref:`tinjau alur kerja <reviews>` dengan "
"peninjau khusus)."

#: admin/access.rst:316
msgid ""
"`Managers` (if you want to delegate most of the management operations to "
"somebody else)."
msgstr ""
"`Pengelola` (jika Anda ingin mendelegasikan sebagian besar operasi "
"pengelolaan kepada orang lain)."

#: admin/access.rst:319
msgid ""
"You should keep all projects configured as `Public` (see :ref:`acl`), "
"otherwise the site-wide permissions provided by membership in the `Users` "
"and `Reviewers` teams won’t have any effect."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus menjaga semua proyek dikonfigurasi sebagai `Publik` "
"(lihat :ref:`acl`), jika tidak, izin di seluruh situs yang disediakan oleh "
"keanggotaan di tim `Pengguna` dan `Peninjau` tidak akan berpengaruh."

#: admin/access.rst:323
msgid ""
"You may also grant some additional permissions of your choice to the default "
"teams. For example, you may want to give a permission to manage screenshots "
"to all the `Users`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat memberikan beberapa izin tambahan pilihan Anda kepada tim "
"bawaan. Misalnya, Anda mungkin ingin memberikan izin untuk mengelola "
"tangkapan layar kepada semua `Pengguna`."

#: admin/access.rst:327
msgid ""
"You can define some new custom teams as well. If you want to keep managing "
"your permissions site-wide for these teams, choose an appropriate value for "
"the :guilabel:`Project selection` (e.g. :guilabel:`All projects` "
"or :guilabel:`All public projects`)."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat mendefinisikan beberapa tim kustom baru. Jika Anda ingin "
"tetap mengelola izin di seluruh situs untuk tim ini, pilih nilai yang sesuai "
"untuk :guilabel:`Pemilihan proyek` (mis. :guilabel:`Pemilihan proyek` "
"atau :guilabel:`Semua proyek publik`)."

#: admin/access.rst:333
msgid "Custom permissions for languages, components or projects"
msgstr "Izin khusus untuk bahasa, komponen, atau proyek"

#: admin/access.rst:335
msgid ""
"You can create your own dedicated teams to manage permissions for distinct "
"objects such as languages, components, and projects. Although these teams "
"can only grant additional privileges, you can’t revoke any permission "
"granted by site-wide or per-project teams by adding another custom team."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membuat tim kustom Anda khusus untuk mengelola izin untuk objek "
"tertentu seperti bahasa, komponen, dan proyek. Meskipun tim ini hanya dapat "
"memberikan hak akses tambahan, Anda tidak dapat mencabut izin apa pun yang "
"diberikan oleh tim di seluruh situs atau per proyek dengan menambahkan tim "
"kustom lainnya."

