#: admin/auth.rst:795
msgid "Configuring third party Django authentication"
msgstr "Mengkonfigurasikan autentikasi Django pihak ketiga"

#: admin/auth.rst:797
msgid ""
"Generally any Django authentication plugin should work with Weblate. Just "
"follow the instructions for the plugin, just remember to keep the Weblate "
"user backend installed."
msgstr ""
"Umumnya setiap pengaya autentikasi Django harus bekerja dengan Weblate. "
"Cukup ikuti petunjuk untuk pengaya tersebut, ingatlah untuk tetap memasang "
"backend pengguna Weblate."

#: admin/auth.rst:806
msgid ""
"Typically the installation will consist of adding an authentication backend "
"to :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS` and installing an "
"authentication app (if there is any) into :setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS`:"
msgstr ""
"Biasanya pemasangan akan terdiri dari penambahan backend autentikasi "
"ke :setting:`django:AUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS` dan memasang aplikasi "
"autentikasi (jika ada) ke dalam :setting:`django:INSTALLED_APPS`:"

#: admin/auth.rst:825
msgid "Two-factor authentication"
msgstr "Autentikasi dua faktor"

#: admin/auth.rst:831
msgid ""
"Two-factor authentication adds another layer of security to your account by "
"requiring more than just a password to sign in."
msgstr ""
"Autentikasi dua faktor menambahkan lapisan keamanan lain pada akun Anda "
"dengan memerlukan lebih dari sekadar kata sandi untuk masuk."

#: admin/auth.rst:833
msgid "Weblate supports the following second factors:"
msgstr "Weblate mendukung faktor kedua berikut:"

#: admin/auth.rst:835
msgid "Security keys (WebAuthn)"
msgstr "Kunci keamanan (WebAuthn)"

#: admin/auth.rst:836
msgid "Both, Passkeys and security keys are supported."
msgstr "Keduanya, Kunci sandi dan kunci keamanan didukung."

#: admin/auth.rst:838
msgid ""
"Passkeys validate your identity using touch, facial recognition, a device "
"password, or a PIN as they include user verification."
msgstr ""
"Kunci sandi memvalidasikan identitas Anda menggunakan sentuhan, pengenalan "
"wajah, kata sandi perangkat, atau PIN karena kunci sandi mencakup verifikasi "
"pengguna."

#: admin/auth.rst:840
msgid ""
"Security keys are WebAuthn credentials that can only be used as a second "
"factor of authentication, and these only validate user presence."
msgstr ""
"Kunci keamanan adalah kredensial WebAuthn yang hanya dapat digunakan sebagai "
"faktor kedua autentikasi, dan ini hanya memvalidasikan keberadaan pengguna."

#: admin/auth.rst:842
msgid "Authenticator apps (TOTP)"
msgstr "Aplikasi autentikator (TOTP)"

#: admin/auth.rst:843
msgid ""
"Authenticator apps and browser extensions like Aegis, Bitwarden, Google "
"Authenticator, 1Password, Authy, Microsoft Authenticator, etc. generate time-"
"based one-time passwords that are used as a second factor to verify your "
"identity when prompted during sign-in."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi autentikator dan ekstensi peramban seperti Aegis, Bitwarden, Google "
"Authenticator, 1Password, Authy, Microsoft Authenticator, dsb. menghasilkan "
"kata sandi sekali pakai berbasis waktu yang digunakan sebagai faktor kedua "
"untuk memverifikasi identitas Anda saat diminta saat masuk."

#: admin/auth.rst:848
msgid "Recovery codes"
msgstr "Kode pemulihan"

#: admin/auth.rst:849
msgid ""
"Recovery codes can be used to access your account if you lose access to your "
"device and cannot receive two-factor authentication codes."
msgstr ""
"Kode pemulihan dapat digunakan untuk mengakses akun Anda jika Anda "
"kehilangan akses ke perangkat dan tidak dapat menerima kode autentikasi dua "
"faktor."

#: admin/auth.rst:851
msgid ""
"Keep your recovery codes as safe as your password. We recommend saving them "
"with a password manager such as Bitwarden, 1Password, Authy, or Keeper."
msgstr ""
"Jaga keamanan kode pemulihan Anda sama seperti keamanan kata sandi Anda. "
"Kami sarankan menyimpannya dengan pengelola kata sandi seperti Bitwarden, "
"1Password, Authy, atau Keeper."

#: admin/auth.rst:855
msgid ""
"Each user can configure this in :ref:`profile-account` and second factor "
"will be required to sign in addition to the existing authentication method."
msgstr ""
"Setiap pengguna dapat mengkonfigurasikan ini di :ref:`profile-account` dan "
"faktor kedua akan diperlukan untuk masuk sebagai tambahan terhadap metode "
"autentikasi yang ada."

#: admin/auth.rst:858
msgid ""
"This can be enforced for users at the project (see :ref:`project-"
"enforced_2fa`) or team level. In site-wide deployments, this can also be "
"used to enforce two-factor authentication for all users by enabling it on "
"the default :guilabel:`Users` team, which is assigned automatically to new "
"users by :ref:`automatic team assignment <autoteam>`."
msgstr ""

#: admin/auth.rst:864
msgid ""
"The permissions of a team with enforced two-factor authentication won't be "
"applied to users who do not have it configured."
msgstr ""
"Izin tim dengan autentikasi dua faktor yang dipaksakan tidak akan diterapkan "
"kepada pengguna yang tidak mengkonfigurasikannya."

#: admin/backup.rst:4
