"Use the generated file to import project when :ref:`adding-projects` or "
"in :wladmin:`import_projectbackup`."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan berkas yang dihasilkan untuk mengimpor proyek saat :ref:`adding-"
"projects` atau di :wladmin:`import_projectbackup`."

#: admin/backup.rst:47
msgid ""
"Restoring of the backup might fail if the restoring server has different set "
"of :ref:`languages` or different configuration "
"of :setting:`SIMPLIFY_LANGUAGES`. The restore will tell you which language "
"codes could not be processed and you can then add missing language "
"definitions manually."
msgstr ""
"Pemulihan cadangan mungkin gagal jika server pemulihan memiliki "
"rangkaian :ref:`languages` yang berbeda atau "
"konfigurasi :setting:`SIMPLIFY_LANGUAGES` yang berbeda. Pemulihan akan "
"memberi tahu Anda kode bahasa mana yang tidak dapat diproses dan Anda "
"kemudian dapat menambahkan definisi bahasa yang hilang secara manual."

#: admin/backup.rst:56
msgid "Automated backup using BorgBackup"
msgstr "Pencadangan otomatis menggunakan BorgBackup"

#: admin/backup.rst:58
msgid ""
"Weblate has built-in support for creating service backups using "
"`BorgBackup`_. Borg creates space-effective encrypted backups which can be "
"safely stored in the cloud. The backups can be controlled in the management "
"interface from the :guilabel:`Backups` tab."
msgstr ""
"Weblate memiliki dukungan bawaan untuk membuat cadangan layanan menggunakan "
"`BorgBackup`_. Borg membuat cadangan terenkripsi hemat ruang yang dapat "
"disimpan dengan aman di awan. Cadangan dapat dikontrol di antarmuka "
"pengelolaan dari tab :guilabel:`Cadangan`."

#: admin/backup.rst:65
msgid "PostgreSQL databases are included in the automated backups."
msgstr "Basis data PostgreSQL disertakan dalam cadangan terotomatis."

#: admin/backup.rst:67
msgid ""
"The backups using Borg are incremental and Weblate is configured to keep "
