#: admin/install.rst:559
msgid "Client IP address"
msgstr "Alamat IP klien"

#: admin/install.rst:560
msgid "This is needed for :ref:`rate-limit` or :ref:`audit-log`."
msgstr "Ini diperlukan untuk :ref:`rate-limit` atau :ref:`audit-log`."

#: admin/install.rst:562
msgid ""
"Weblate parses IP address from the ``REMOTE_ADDR``, which is set by the WSGI "
"handler. This might be empty (when using socket for WSGI) or contain a "
"reverse proxy address, so Weblate needs an additional HTTP header with a "
"client IP address."
msgstr ""
"Weblate mengurai alamat IP dari ``REMOTE_ADDR``, yang diatur oleh pengendali "
"WSGI. Alamat ini mungkin kosong (ketika menggunakan soket untuk WSGI) atau "
"berisi alamat proksi terbalik, sehingga Weblate memerlukan kepala HTTP "
"tambahan dengan alamat IP klien."

#: admin/install.rst:567
msgid ""
"Enabling :setting:`IP_BEHIND_REVERSE_PROXY` should be sufficient for the "
"most usual setups, but you might need to adjust :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` "
"and :setting:`IP_PROXY_OFFSET` as well "
"(use :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_HEADER` and :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_OFFSET` "
"in the Docker container)."
msgstr ""
"Mengaktifkan :setting:`IP_BEHIND_REVERSE_PROXY` seharusnya cukup untuk "
"pengaturan paling umum, tetapi Anda mungkin perlu "
"menyesuaikan :setting:`IP_PROXY_HEADER` dan :setting:`IP_PROXY_OFFSET` juga "
"(gunakan :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_HEADER` "
"dan :envvar:`WEBLATE_IP_PROXY_OFFSET` dalam kontainer Docker)."

#: admin/install.rst:574
msgid ""
"This configuration cannot be turned on by default, because it would allow IP "
"address spoofing on installations that don't have a properly configured "
"reverse proxy."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi ini tidak dapat diaktifkan secara bawaan, karena akan "
"memungkinkan pemalsuan alamat IP pada pemasangan yang tidak memiliki proksi "
"terbalik yang dikonfigurasi dengan benar."

#: admin/install.rst:578
msgid "Server host name"
msgstr "Nama hos server"

#: admin/install.rst:579
msgid ""
"The :http:header:`Host` header should match to whatever is configured "
"as :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN`. Additional configuration might be needed in your "
"reverse proxy (for example use ``ProxyPreserveHost On`` for Apache or "
"``proxy_set_header Host $host;`` with nginx)."
msgstr ""
"Kepala :http:header:`Host` harus sesuai dengan konfigurasi yang "
"didefinisikan sebagai :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN`. Konfigurasi tambahan mungkin "
"diperlukan di proksi terbalik Anda (misalnya, gunakan ``ProxyPreserveHost "
"On`` untuk Apache atau ``proxy_set_header Host $host;`` dengan nginx)."

#: admin/install.rst:586
msgid ""
"CSRF verification failed errors are often caused by a mismatch between "
"the :http:header:`Host` header and configured :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN`."
msgstr ""
"Galat verifikasi CSRF yang gagal sering kali disebabkan oleh ketidakcocokan "
"antara kepala :http:header:`Host` dan :setting:`SITE_DOMAIN` yang "
"dikonfigurasikan."

#: admin/install.rst:589
msgid "Client protocol"
msgstr "Protokol klien"

#: admin/install.rst:590
msgid ""
"Not passing correct protocol may cause Weblate to end up in redirection loop "
"trying to upgrade client to HTTPS. Make sure it is correctly exposed by the "
"reverse proxy as :http:header:`X-Forwarded-Proto`."
msgstr ""
"Tidak melewati protokol yang benar dapat menyebabkan Weblate terjebak dalam "
"loop pengalihan saat mencoba meningkatkan klien ke HTTPS. Pastikan protokol "
"tersebut diekspos dengan benar oleh proksi terbalik sebagai :http:header:`X-"
"Forwarded-Proto`."

#: admin/install.rst:594
msgid ""
"This header then needs to be configured "
"in :setting:`django:SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (:file:`settings.py`) "
"or :envvar:`WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (Docker environment)."
msgstr ""
"Kepala ini kemudian perlu dikonfigurasikan "
"dalam :setting:`django:SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (:file:`settings.py`) "
"atau :envvar:`WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER` (lingkungan Docker)."

#: admin/install.rst:600
msgid ""
"The header value is case-sensitive in the configuration, so "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,https`` and "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,HTTPS`` are not "
"interchangeable."
msgstr ""
"Nilai kepala peka huruf kapital dalam konfigurasi, jadi "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,https`` dan "
"``WEBLATE_SECURE_PROXY_SSL_HEADER=HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO,HTTPS`` tidak dapat "
"dipertukarkan."

#: admin/install.rst:607
msgid ""
"If you are getting a \"Too many redirects\" error from the browser, this is "
"most likely caused by mismatch between the actual protocol (HTTPS) and what "
"is observed by Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda mendapatkan galat \"Terlalu banyak pengalihan\" dari peramban, "
"kemungkinan besar ini disebabkan oleh ketidakcocokan antara protokol aktual "
"(HTTPS) dan apa yang diamati oleh Weblate."

#: admin/install.rst:613
msgid ""
"The protocol proxy headers are automatically handled by :program:`gunicorn` "
"in the default configuration, but other WSGI servers have more secure "
"configuration and require explicit setting of this."
msgstr ""
"Kepala proksi protokol secara otomatis ditangani oleh :program:`gunicorn` "
"dalam konfigurasi bawaan, tetapi server WSGI lainnya memiliki konfigurasi "
"yang lebih aman dan memerlukan pengaturan eksplisit ini."

#: admin/install.rst:617
