#: admin/install.rst:1754
msgid ""
"Everything else is integrated automatically, you will now collect both "
"server and client side errors."
msgstr ""
"Segala sesuatu lainnya terintegrasi secara otomatis, Anda sekarang akan "
"mengumpulkan galat sisi server dan klien."

#: admin/install.rst:1759
msgid ""
"Error logging also includes exceptions that were gracefully handled, but "
"might indicate a problem - such as failed parsing of an uploaded file."
msgstr ""
"Pencatatan galat juga mencakup pengecualian yang ditangani dengan baik, "
"tetapi mungkin menunjukkan adanya masalah - seperti kegagalan penguraian "
"berkas yang diunggah."

#: admin/install.rst:1765
msgid "Graylog log management"
msgstr "Pengelolaan catatan Graylog"

#: admin/install.rst:1769
msgid ""
"Weblate can be configured to log using the GELF TCP protocol. This was "
"developed for Graylog integration, but can be used with any compliant "
"logging platform."
msgstr ""
"Weblate dapat dikonfigurasikan untuk melakukan pencatatan menggunakan "
"protokol TCP GELF. Ini dikembangkan untuk integrasi Graylog, tetapi dapat "
"digunakan dengan platform pencatatan apa pun yang kompatibel."

#: admin/install.rst:1772
msgid ""
"The configuration boilerplate is included in :ref:`sample-configuration`, "
"for Docker this can be configured using :envvar:`WEBLATE_LOG_GELF_HOST`."
msgstr ""
"Boilerplate konfigurasi disertakan dalam :ref:`sample-configuration`, untuk "
"Docker ini dapat dikonfigurasikan "
"menggunakan :envvar:`WEBLATE_LOG_GELF_HOST`."

#: admin/install.rst:1776
msgid "Migrating Weblate to another server"
msgstr "Memigrasikan Weblate ke server lain"

#: admin/install.rst:1778
msgid ""
"Migrating Weblate to another server should be pretty easy, however it stores "
"data in few locations which you should migrate carefully. The best approach "
"is to stop Weblate for the migration."
msgstr ""
"Memigrasikan Weblate ke server lain seharusnya cukup mudah, tetapi data "
"disimpan di beberapa lokasi yang perlu Anda migrasikan dengan hati-hati. "
"Pendekatan terbaik adalah menghentikan Weblate untuk migrasi."

#: admin/install.rst:1783
msgid "Migrating database"
msgstr "Memigrasikan basis data"

#: admin/install.rst:1785
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Depending on your database backend, you might have several options to "
#| "migrate the database. The most straightforward approach is to use "
#| "database native tools, as they are usually the most effective "
#| "(e.g. :command:`mysqldump` or :command:`pg_dump`). Alternatively you can "
#| "use replication in case your database supports it."
msgid ""
"The most straightforward approach is to use database native tools, as they "
"are usually the most effective (e.g. :command:`pg_dump`). Alternatively you "
"can use replication if your database supports it."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada basis data Anda, Anda mungkin memiliki beberapa opsi untuk "
"memigrasikan basis data. Pendekatan yang paling mudah adalah menggunakan "
"alat bawaan basis data, karena biasanya paling efektif "
"(misalnya :command:`mysqldump` atau :command:`pg_dump`). Sebagai alternatif, "
"Anda dapat menggunakan replikasi jika basis data Anda mendukungnya."

#: admin/install.rst:1791
msgid "Migrating between databases described in :ref:`database-migration`."
msgstr ""
"Memigrasikan antar basis data dijelaskan dalam :ref:`database-migration`."

#: admin/install.rst:1794
msgid "Migrating VCS repositories"
msgstr "Memigrasikan repositori VCS"

#: admin/install.rst:1796
msgid ""
"The VCS repositories stored under :setting:`DATA_DIR` need to be migrated as "
"well. You can simply copy them or use :command:`rsync` to do the migration "
"more effectively."
msgstr ""
"Repositori VCS yang disimpan di bawah :setting:`DATA_DIR` juga perlu "
"dimigrasikan. Anda cukup menyalinnya atau menggunakan :command:`rsync` untuk "
"melakukan migrasi dengan lebih efektif."

#: admin/install.rst:1801
msgid "Other notes"
msgstr "Catatan lainnya"

#: admin/install.rst:1803
msgid ""
"Don't forget to move other services Weblate might have been using like "
"Valkey, Redis, Cron jobs or custom authentication backends."
msgstr ""
"Jangan lupa untuk memindahkan layanan lain yang mungkin digunakan Weblate "
"seperti Valkey, Redis, pekerjaan Cron atau backend autentikasi kustom."

#: admin/install/docker.rst:2
msgid "Installing using Docker"
msgstr "Memasang menggunakan Docker"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:4
msgid ""
"With dockerized Weblate deployment you can get your personal Weblate "
"instance up and running in seconds. All of Weblate's dependencies are "
"already included. PostgreSQL is set up as the default database and Valkey as "
"a caching backend."
msgstr ""
"Dengan penyebaran Weblate yang terdokerisasi, Anda dapat langsung "
"menjalankan instansi Weblate pribadi Anda dalam hitungan detik. Semua "
"dependensi Weblate sudah disertakan. PostgreSQL diatur sebagai basis data "
"bawaan dan Valkey sebagai backend simpanan."

