#: admin/install/docker.rst:368
msgid ""
"After container setup, you can sign in as `admin` user with password "
"provided in :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD`, or a random password generated "
"on first start if that was not set."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengaturan kontainer, Anda dapat masuk sebagai pengguna `admin` "
"dengan kata sandi yang diberikan di :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD`, atau "
"kata sandi acak yang dibuat saat pertama kali memulai jika tidak diatur."

#: admin/install/docker.rst:372
msgid ""
"To reset `admin` password, restart the container "
"with :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD` set to new password."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur ulang kata sandi `admin`, mulai ulang kontainer "
"dengan :envvar:`WEBLATE_ADMIN_PASSWORD` yang diatur ke kata sandi baru."

#: admin/install/docker.rst:382
msgid "Number of processes and memory consumption"
msgstr "Jumlah proses dan konsumsi memori"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:384
msgid ""
"The number of worker processes for both WSGI and Celery is determined "
"automatically based on number of CPUs. This works well for most cloud "
"virtual machines as these typically have few CPUs and good amount of memory."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah proses pekerja untuk WSGI dan Celery ditentukan secara otomatis "
"berdasarkan jumlah CPU. Hal ini berfungsi dengan baik untuk sebagian besar "
"mesin virtual cloud karena biasanya memiliki CPU yang sedikit dan memori "
"yang memadai."

#: admin/install/docker.rst:388
msgid ""
"In case you have a lot of CPU cores and hit out of memory issues, try "
"reducing number of workers:"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda memiliki banyak inti CPU dan mengalami isu memori, coba kurangi "
"jumlah worker:"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:396
msgid "You can also fine-tune individual worker categories:"
msgstr "Anda juga dapat menyempurnakan kategori pekerja individual:"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:409
msgid ""
"The prefetch multiplier controls how many tasks each worker execution slot "
"can reserve. The default of one avoids reserving additional long-running or "
"payload-heavy tasks. The notification worker uses four in this example "
"because its short tasks can benefit from buffering. Increase the value only "
"after measuring queue latency and worker memory usage."
msgstr ""

#: admin/install/docker.rst:415
msgid ""
"Memory usage can be further reduced by running only a single Celery process:"
msgstr ""
"Penggunaan memori dapat dikurangi lebih lanjut dengan hanya menjalankan satu "
"proses Celery:"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:438
msgid "Scaling horizontally"
msgstr "Menskalakan secara horizontal"

#: admin/install/docker.rst:442
msgid ""
"You can run multiple Weblate containers to scale the service horizontally. "
"The :file:`/app/data` volume has to be shared by all containers, it is "
"recommended to use cluster filesystem such as GlusterFS for this. "
"The :file:`/app/cache` volume should be separate for each container."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menjalankan beberapa kontainer Weblate untuk menskalakan layanan "
"secara horizontal. Volume :file:`/app/data` harus digunakan bersama oleh "
"semua kontainer. Disarankan untuk menggunakan sistem berkas klaster seperti "
"GlusterFS untuk ini. Volume :file:`/app/cache` harus terpisah untuk setiap "
"kontainer."

#: admin/install/docker.rst:447
msgid ""
"Each Weblate container has defined role using :envvar:`WEBLATE_SERVICE` "
"environment variable. Please follow carefully the documentation as some of "
"the services should be running just once in the cluster, and the order of "
"the services matters as well."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kontainer Weblate memiliki peran yang ditentukan menggunakan variabel "
"lingkungan :envvar:`WEBLATE_SERVICE`. Harap ikuti dokumentasi dengan saksama "
"karena beberapa layanan hanya boleh dijalankan sekali dalam klaster, dan "
"urutan layanan juga penting."

#: admin/install/docker.rst:452
msgid ""
"You can find example setup in the ``docker-compose`` repo as `docker-compose-"
"split.yml <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/docker-compose/blob/main/docker-"
"compose-split.yml>`__."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menemukan contoh pengaturan di repo ``docker-compose`` sebagai "
"`docker-compose-split.yml <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/docker-compose/blob/"
"main/docker-compose-split.yml>`__."

