#: admin/management.rst:559
msgid ""
"Batch imports components into project based on the file mask. It is based on "
"the :ref:`addon-weblate.discovery.discovery` add-on, so you might want to "
"use that instead."
msgstr ""
"Mengimpor komponen secara penjumlahan ke dalam proyek berdasarkan mask "
