msgid "Several new translations."
msgstr "Beberapa terjemahan baru."

#: changes/v0.rst:79
msgid "Improved merging of upstream changes."
msgstr "Meningkatkan penggabungan perubahan hulu."

#: changes/v0.rst:80
msgid "Better handle concurrent git pull and translation."
