msgid "API now reports rate limiting status in the HTTP headers."
msgstr "API sekarang melaporkan status pembatasan akses di kepala HTTP."

#: changes/v4.rst:1160
msgid "Added support for Google Translate V3 API (Advanced)."
msgstr "Menambahkan dukungan untuk API Google Translate V3 (Lanjutan)."

#: changes/v4.rst:1161
msgid "Added ability to restrict access on component level."
msgstr "Menambahkan kemampuan untuk membatasi akses pada tingkat komponen."

#: changes/v4.rst:1162
msgid ""
"Added support for whitespace and other special chars in translation flags, "
"see :ref:`custom-checks`."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan dukungan untuk spasi dan karakter khusus lainnya dalam tanda "
"terjemahan, lihat :ref:`custom-checks`."

#: changes/v4.rst:1163
msgid "Always show rendered text check if enabled."
msgstr "Selalu tampilkan centang teks yang ditampilkan jika diaktifkan."

#: changes/v4.rst:1164
msgid "API now supports filtering of changes."
msgstr "API sekarang mendukung pemfilteran perubahan."

#: changes/v4.rst:1165
msgid "Added support for sharing glossaries between projects."
msgstr "Menambahkan dukungan untuk berbagi glosarium antar proyek."

#: changes/v4.rst:1173
msgid ""
"There are several changes in :file:`settings_example.py`, most notable "
"middleware changes, please adjust your settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Ada beberapa perubahan dalam :file:`settings_example.py`, sebagian besar "
"perubahan alat tengah yang penting, harap sesuaikan pengaturan Anda."

#: changes/v4.rst:1175
msgid ""
"There are new quality checks, you might want to include them in case you "
"modified the :setting:`CHECK_LIST`."
msgstr ""
"Ada pemeriksaan kualitas baru, Anda mungkin ingin menyertakannya jika Anda "
"mengubah :setting:`CHECK_LIST`."

#: changes/v4.rst:1176
msgid ""
"There is change in ``DEFAULT_THROTTLE_CLASSES`` setting to allow reporting "
"of rate limiting in the API."
msgstr ""
"Ada perubahan dalam pengaturan ``DEFAULT_THROTTLE_CLASSES`` untuk "
"mengizinkan pelaporan pembatasan akses dalam API."

#: changes/v4.rst:1179
msgid ""
"The ``MT_DEEPL_API_VERSION`` setting has been removed in Version 4.7. "
"The :ref:`mt-deepl` machine translation now uses the new "
"``MT_DEEPL_API_URL`` instead. You might need to adjust ``MT_DEEPL_API_URL`` "
"to match your subscription."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ``MT_DEEPL_API_VERSION`` telah dihapus di Versi 4.7. Terjemahan "
"mesin :ref:`mt-deepl` sekarang menggunakan ``MT_DEEPL_API_URL`` yang baru. "
"Anda mungkin perlu menyesuaikan ``MT_DEEPL_API_URL`` agar sesuai dengan "
"langganan Anda."

