#: changes/v5.rst:2149
msgid ""
"The default value of :setting:`IP_PROXY_OFFSET` has been changed from 1 to "
"-1."
msgstr ""
"Nilai bawaan :setting:`IP_PROXY_OFFSET` telah diubah dari 1 menjadi -1."

#: changes/v5.rst:2157
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/103?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`Semua perubahan secara rinci <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/"
"milestone/103?closed=1>`__."

#: changes/v5.rst:2160
msgid "Weblate 5.0"
msgstr "Weblate 5.0"

#: changes/v5.rst:2162
msgid "*Released on August 24th 2023.*"
msgstr "*Dirilis pada 24 Agustus 2023.*"

#: changes/v5.rst:2166
msgid ":doc:`/formats/markdown` support, thanks to Anders Kaplan."
msgstr ":doc:`/formats/markdown` dukungan, berkat Anders Kaplan."

#: changes/v5.rst:2167
msgid ":ref:`category` can now organize components within a project."
msgstr ":ref:`category` sekarang dapat mengorganisir komponen dalam proyek."

#: changes/v5.rst:2168
msgid ""
":doc:`/formats/fluent` now has better syntax checks thanks to Henry Wilkes."
msgstr ""
":doc:`/formats/fluent` sekarang memiliki pemeriksaan sintaksis yang lebih "
"baik berkat Henry Wilkes."

#: changes/v5.rst:2169
msgid "Inviting users now works with all authentication methods."
msgstr ""
"Mengundang pengguna sekarang berfungsi dengan semua metode autentikasi."

#: changes/v5.rst:2170
msgid ""
"Docker container supports file backed secrets, see :ref:`docker-secrets`."
msgstr ""
"Kontainer Docker mendukung rahasia yang didukung berkas, lihat :ref:`docker-"
"secrets`."

#: changes/v5.rst:2174
msgid "Plurals handling in machine translation."
msgstr "Penanganan jamak dalam terjemahan mesin."

#: changes/v5.rst:2175
msgid ""
":ref:`check-same` check now honors placeholders even in the strict mode."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-same` pemeriksaan sekarang menghormati pengganti bahkan dalam "
"mode ketat."

#: changes/v5.rst:2176
msgid ""
":ref:`check-reused` is no longer triggered for languages with a single "
"plural form."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-reused` tidak lagi dipicu untuk bahasa dengan bentuk jamak "
"tunggal."

#: changes/v5.rst:2177
msgid "WebP is now supported for :ref:`screenshots`."
msgstr "WebP sekarang didukung untuk :ref:`screenshots`."

#: changes/v5.rst:2178
msgid ""
"Avoid duplicate notification when a user is subscribed to overlapping scopes."
msgstr ""
"Hindari notifikasi ganda saat pengguna berlangganan pada cakupan yang "
"tumpang tindih."

#: changes/v5.rst:2179
msgid "OCR support for non-English languages in :ref:`screenshots`."
msgstr "Dukungan OCR untuk bahasa non-Inggris di :ref:`screenshots`."

#: changes/v5.rst:2180
msgid ":ref:`xliff` now supports displaying source string location."
msgstr ":ref:`xliff` sekarang mendukung tampilan lokasi string sumber."

#: changes/v5.rst:2181
msgid ""
"Rendering strings with plurals, placeholders or alternative translations."
msgstr ""
"Merender string dengan bentuk jamak, pengganti, atau terjemahan alternatif."

#: changes/v5.rst:2182
msgid "User API now includes last sign in date."
msgstr "API Pengguna sekarang menyertakan tanggal masuk terakhir."

#: changes/v5.rst:2183
msgid "User API token is now hidden for privacy reasons by default."
msgstr ""
"Token API Pengguna sekarang disembunyikan karena alasan privasi secara "
"bawaan."

#: changes/v5.rst:2184
msgid "Faster adding terms to glossary."
msgstr "Menambahkan istilah ke glosarium lebih cepat."

#: changes/v5.rst:2185
msgid ""
"Better preserve translation on source file change in :doc:`/formats/html` "
"and :doc:`/formats/txt`."
msgstr ""
"Lebih baik pertahankan terjemahan pada perubahan berkas sumber di :doc:`/"
"formats/html` dan :doc:`/formats/txt`."

#: changes/v5.rst:2186
msgid "Added indication of automatic assignment to team listing."
msgstr "Menambahkan indikasi penugasan otomatis ke daftar tim."

#: changes/v5.rst:2187
msgid "Users now have to confirm invitations to become team members."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna sekarang harus mengkonfirmasikan undangan untuk menjadi anggota tim."

#: changes/v5.rst:2188
msgid ""
":ref:`check-formats` can now check all plural forms with the ``strict-"
"format`` flag."
msgstr ""
":ref:`check-formats` sekarang dapat memeriksa semua bentuk jamak dengan "
"tanda ``strict-format``."

#: changes/v5.rst:2189
msgid ":doc:`/user/checks` browsing experience."
msgstr ":doc:`/user/checks` pengalaman menelusuri."

#: changes/v5.rst:2190
msgid "Highlight differences in the source string in automatic suggestions."
msgstr "Sorot perbedaan dalam string sumber di saran otomatis."

#: changes/v5.rst:2191
msgid "Visual diff now better understands compositing characters."
msgstr "Visual diff sekarang lebih memahami pengomposisian karakter."

#: changes/v5.rst:2195
msgid "User names handling while committing to Git."
msgstr "Penanganan nama pengguna saat mengkomit pada Git."

#: changes/v5.rst:2196
msgid ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.cleanup.blank` and :ref:`addon-weblate.cleanup.generic` "
"now remove all strings at once."
msgstr ""
":ref:`addon-weblate.cleanup.blank` dan :ref:`addon-weblate.cleanup.generic` "
"sekarang menghapus semua string sekaligus."

#: changes/v5.rst:2197
msgid "Language filtering in :doc:`/devel/reporting`."
msgstr "Pemfilteran bahasa di :doc:`/devel/reporting`."

#: changes/v5.rst:2198
msgid ""
"Reduced false positives of :ref:`check-reused` when fixing the translation."
msgstr ""
"Mengurangi positif palsu :ref:`check-reused` saat memperbaiki terjemahan."

#: changes/v5.rst:2199
msgid "Fixed caching issues after updating screenshots from the repository."
msgstr ""
"Memperbaiki isu penyimpanan setelah memperbarui tangkapan layar dari "
"repositori."

#: changes/v5.rst:2203
msgid "Python 3.9 or newer is now required."
msgstr "Python 3.9 atau yang lebih baru sekarang diperlukan."

#: changes/v5.rst:2204
msgid "Several UI URLs have been changed to be able to handle categories."
msgstr "Beberapa URL UI telah diubah untuk dapat menangani kategori."

#: changes/v5.rst:2210
msgid ""
"There are several changes in :file:`settings_example.py`, most notable is "
"changes in ``CACHES`` and ``SOCIAL_AUTH_PIPELINE``, please adjust your "
"settings accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Ada beberapa perubahan dalam :file:`settings_example.py`, yang paling "
"menonjol adalah perubahan dalam ``CACHES`` dan ``SOCIAL_AUTH_PIPELINE``, "
"silakan sesuaikan pengaturan Anda."

#: changes/v5.rst:2211
msgid "Several previously optional dependencies are now required."
msgstr "Beberapa dependensi yang sebelumnya opsional sekarang diperlukan."

#: changes/v5.rst:2212
msgid ""
"The database upgrade can take considerable time on larger sites due to "
"structure changes."
msgstr ""
"Peningkatan basis data dapat memerlukan waktu yang cukup lama pada situs "
"yang lebih besar karena perubahan struktur."

#: changes/v5.rst:2215
msgid ""
"`All changes in detail <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/milestone/99?"
"closed=1>`__."
msgstr ""
"`Semua perubahan secara rinci <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate/"
"milestone/99?closed=1>`__."

