#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:86
msgid "Enable 2FA for all admin-level accounts."
msgstr "Aktifkan 2FA untuk semua akun tingkat admin."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:87
msgid ""
"Keep the Weblate instance and its dependencies (Python, Django, Celery, "
"database, etc.) up to date."
msgstr ""
"Jaga agar instansi Weblate dan dependensinya (Python, Django, Celery, basis "
"data, dll.) tetap terkini."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:88
msgid ""
"Integrate with SIEM systems using the GELF protocol for audit and "
"application log forwarding."
msgstr ""
"Integrasikan dengan sistem SIEM menggunakan protokol GELF untuk audit dan "
"penerusan catatan aplikasi."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:91
msgid "Identification"
