msgstr ""
"**Penilaian PII:** DPO menentukan apakah pelanggaran memerlukan notifikasi "
"GDPR 72 jam."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:134
msgid "Reintroduce services in a phased approach."
msgstr "Perkenalkan kembali layanan secara bertahap."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:135
msgid ""
"Confirm the root cause has been removed or a compensating control is in "
"place before restoring normal traffic."
msgstr ""

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:137
msgid ""
"Rotate affected credentials and verify integrity of the restored system, "
"repositories, and configuration."
msgstr ""

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:139
msgid "The Security Officer and IRL approve returning to normal operations."
msgstr ""

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:140
msgid ""
"Monitor logs and system behavior continuously for at least 72 hours post-"
"recovery."
msgstr ""
"Pantau catatan dan perilaku sistem secara terus-menerus setidaknya selama 72 "
"jam pasca-pemulihan."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:143
msgid "Post-incident review"
msgstr "Tinjauan pasca-insiden"

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:145
msgid ""
"**Timeline:** Hold a review meeting within **5 business days** of incident "
"closure."
msgstr ""
"**Garis Waktu:** Mengadakan pertemuan peninjauan dalam **5 hari bisnis** "
"setelah penutupan insiden."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:146
msgid "Compile a full incident timeline and actions taken."
msgstr "Susun garis waktu insiden lengkap dan tindakan yang diambil."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:147
msgid ""
"Perform Root Cause Analysis (RCA) and document it within **10 business "
"days**."
msgstr ""
"Lakukan Root Cause Analysis (RCA) dan dokumentasikan dalam **10 hari "
"bisnis**."

#: security/incident-response-plan.rst:148
msgid "Update security policies and IRP documentation based on findings."
msgstr "Perbarui kebijakan keamanan dan dokumentasi IRP berdasarkan temuan."

