msgid ""
"The recommended Weblate configuration uses Argon2 with time_cost = 2, "
"memory_cost = 102400, and parallelism = 8."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi Weblate yang direkomendasikan menggunakan Argon2 dengan "
"time_cost = 2, memory_cost = 102400, dan parallelism = 8."

