msgid ""
"The password hashing can be customized "
"using :setting:`django:PASSWORD_HASHERS`."
msgstr ""
"Hashing kata sandi dapat disesuaikan "
"menggunakan :setting:`django:PASSWORD_HASHERS`."

#: security/passwords.rst:16
msgid "Password validation"
msgstr "Validasi kata sandi"

#: security/passwords.rst:18
msgid ""
"When a user is configuring a password, it is validated to reduce the risk of "
"using weak passwords."
msgstr ""
"Saat pengguna mengkonfigurasikan kata sandi, kata sandi tersebut divalidasi "
"untuk mengurangi risiko penggunaan kata sandi yang lemah."

