"is ``<YEAR>.<MONTH>.<PATCH>`` with a numeric, non-zero-padded month. The "
"``<PATCH>`` part is omitted for the first release in a month when it would "
"be ``0``, for example ``2026.5``. Patch releases use the full version "
"number, for example ``2026.5.1``."
msgstr ""

#: security/releases.rst:21
msgid ""
