#: snippets/vcs-credentials.rst:1
msgid ""
"The configuration dictionary consists of credentials defined for each API "
"host. The layout is same for almost all version control integrations and is "
"described at :ref:`settings-credentials`."
msgstr ""
"Kamus konfigurasi terdiri dari kredensial yang ditentukan untuk setiap hos "
"API. Tata letaknya sama untuk hampir semua integrasi kontrol versi dan "
"dijelaskan di :ref:`settings-credentials`."

#: user/checks.rst:4
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The quality checks help catch common translator errors, ensuring the "
#| "translation is in good shape. The checks can be ignored in case of false "
#| "positives."
msgid ""
"The quality checks help catch common translator errors, ensuring the "
"translation is in good shape. The checks can be ignored in case of false "
"positives. For practical translation guidance around placeholders, markup, "
"punctuation, and plural forms, see :ref:`translating-special-text`."
msgstr ""
"Pemeriksaan kualitas membantu mendeteksi galat umum penerjemah, memastikan "
"terjemahan dalam kondisi baik. Pemeriksaan ini dapat diabaikan jika terjadi "
"kesalahan positif."

#: user/checks.rst:9
msgid ""
"Once submitting a translation with a failing check, this is immediately "
"shown to the user:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengirimkan terjemahan dengan pemeriksaan gagal, ini segera "
"ditunjukkan kepada pengguna:"

#: user/checks.rst:18
msgid "Automatic fixups"
msgstr "Perbaikan otomatis"

#: user/checks.rst:20
msgid ""
"In addition to :ref:`checks`, Weblate can fix some common errors in "
"translated strings automatically. Use it with caution to not have it add "
"errors."
msgstr ""
"Selain :ref:`checks`, Weblate dapat memperbaiki beberapa galat umum dalam "
"string terjemahan secara otomatis. Gunakan dengan hati-hati agar tidak "
"menambah galat."

#: user/checks.rst:29
msgid "Trailing ellipsis replacer"
msgstr "Pengganti elipsis di belakang"

#: user/checks.rst:0
msgid "Class name"
msgstr "Nama kelas"

#: user/checks.rst:33
msgid ""
"Replace trailing dots (``...``) with an ellipsis (``…``) to make it "
"consistent with the source string."
msgstr ""
"Ganti titik di akhir (``...``) dengan elipsis (``…``) agar konsisten dengan "
"string sumber."

#: user/checks.rst:37
msgid "Zero-width space removal"
msgstr "Penghapusan spasi lebar-nol"

#: user/checks.rst:41
msgid ""
"Zero width space is typically not desired in the translation. This fix will "
"remove it unless it is present in the source string as well."
msgstr ""
"Spasi dengan lebar nol biasanya tidak diinginkan dalam terjemahan. Perbaikan "
"ini akan menghapusnya kecuali jika spasi tersebut juga ada dalam string "
"sumber."

#: user/checks.rst:45
msgid "Control characters removal"
msgstr "Penghapusan karakter kontrol"

#: user/checks.rst:49
msgid "Removes control characters if the source does not contain any."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus karakter kontrol jika sumber tidak mengandung karakter apa pun."

#: user/checks.rst:52
msgid "Devanagari danda"
msgstr "Dewanagari danda"

#: user/checks.rst:56
msgid ""
"Replaces sentence full stop in Bangla by the Devanagari danda character (``।"
"``)."
msgstr ""
"Mengganti titik dalam kalimat dalam Bangla dengan karakter danda Devanagari "
"(``।``)."

#: user/checks.rst:67
msgid "Ensures French uses correct punctuation spacing."
msgstr "Memastikan Prancis menggunakan spasi tanda baca yang benar."

#: user/checks.rst:69
msgid ""
"This fixup can be disabled via ``ignore-punctuation-spacing`` flag (which "
"also disables :ref:`check-punctuation-spacing`)."
msgstr ""
"Perbaikan ini dapat dinonaktifkan melalui penanda ``ignore-punctuation-"
"spacing`` (yang juga menonaktifkan :ref:`check-punctuation-spacing`)."

#: user/checks.rst:75
msgid "Unsafe HTML cleanup"
msgstr "Pembersihan HTML yang tidak aman"

#: user/checks.rst:79
msgid "Removes unsafe HTML markup from strings flagged as ``safe-html``."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus markah HTML yang tidak aman dari string yang ditandai sebagai "
"``safe-html``."

#: user/checks.rst:86
msgid "Trailing and leading whitespace fixer"
msgstr "Pemecah spasi awal dan akhir"

#: user/checks.rst:90
msgid ""
"Makes leading and trailing whitespace consistent with the source string. The "
"behavior can be fine-tuned using ``ignore-begin-space`` and ``ignore-end-"
"space`` flags to skip processing parts of the string."
msgstr ""
"Membuat spasi awal dan akhir konsisten dengan string sumber. Perilaku ini "
"dapat diatur dengan baik menggunakan penanda ``ignore-begin-space`` dan "
"``ignore-end-space`` untuk melewati pemrosesan bagian string."

#: user/checks.rst:97
msgid "Quality checks"
msgstr "Pemeriksaan kualitas"

#: user/checks.rst:99
msgid ""
"Weblate employs a wide range of quality checks on strings. The following "
"section describes them all in further detail. There are also language "
"specific checks. Please file a bug if anything is reported in error."
msgstr ""
"Weblate menggunakan berbagai pemeriksaan kualitas pada string. Bagian "
"berikut menjelaskan semuanya secara lebih rinci. Terdapat juga pemeriksaan "
"khusus bahasa. Silakan laporkan kerusakan jika terdapat galat yang "
"dilaporkan."

#: user/files.rst:2
msgid "Downloading and uploading translations"
msgstr "Mengunduh dan mengunggah terjemahan"

#: user/files.rst:4
msgid ""
"You can export files from a translation, make changes, and import them "
"again. This allows working offline, and then merging changes back into the "
"existing translation. This works even if it has been changed in the meantime."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengekspor berkas dari terjemahan, membuat perubahan, dan "
"mengimpornya kembali. Ini memungkinkan Anda bekerja secara luring, lalu "
"menggabungkan kembali perubahan ke dalam terjemahan yang sudah ada. Ini "
"tetap berlaku meskipun terjemahan telah diubah."

#: user/files.rst:10
msgid ""
"Available options might be limited by :ref:`access control <access-control>` "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Pilihan yang tersedia mungkin dibatasi oleh pengaturan :ref:`kontrol akses "
"<access-control>`."

#: user/files.rst:16
msgid "Downloading translations"
msgstr "Mengunduh terjemahan"

#: user/files.rst:18
msgid ""
"From the project or component dashboard, translatable files can be "
"downloaded in the :guilabel:`Files` menu."
msgstr ""
"Dari dasbor proyek atau komponen, berkas yang dapat diterjemahkan dapat "
"diunduh di menu :guilabel:`Berkas`."

#: user/files.rst:21
msgid ""
"The first option is to download the file in the original format as it is "
"stored in the repository. In this case, any pending changes in the "
"translation are getting committed and the up-to-date file is yield without "
"any conversions."
msgstr ""
"Opsi pertama adalah mengunduh berkas dalam format asli sebagaimana tersimpan "
"di repositori. Dengan cara ini, setiap perubahan yang tertunda dalam "
"terjemahan akan diproses dan berkas terbaru akan dihasilkan tanpa konversi "
"apa pun."

#: user/files.rst:25
msgid ""
"You can also download the translation converted into one of the widely used "
"localization formats. The converted files will be enriched with data "
"provided in Weblate; such as additional context, comments or flags. Several "
"file formats are available via the :guilabel:`Files` ↓ :guilabel:`Customize "
"download` menu:"
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat mengunduh terjemahan yang telah dikonversi ke salah satu "
"format lokalisasi yang umum digunakan. Berkas yang dikonversi akan diperkaya "
"dengan data yang disediakan di Weblate; seperti konteks tambahan, komentar, "
"atau tanda. Beberapa format berkas tersedia melalui menu :guilabel:`Berkas` "
"↓ :guilabel:`Sesuaikan unduhan`:"

#: user/files.rst:30
msgid "gettext PO (``po``)"
msgstr "PO gettext (``po``)"

#: user/files.rst:31
msgid "XLIFF 1.1 with gettext extensions (``xliff``)"
msgstr "XLIFF 1.1 dengan ekstensi gettext (``xliff``)"

#: user/files.rst:32
msgid "XLIFF 1.1 (``xliff11``)"
msgstr "XLIFF 1.1 (``xliff11``)"

#: user/files.rst:33
msgid "TermBase eXchange (``tbx``)"
msgstr "TermBase eXchange (``tbx``)"

#: user/files.rst:34
msgid "Translation Memory eXchange (``tmx``)"
msgstr "Memori Terjemahan eXchange (``tmx``)"

#: user/files.rst:35
msgid ""
"gettext MO (only available when translation is using gettext PO) (``mo``)"
msgstr ""
"gettext MO (hanya tersedia saat terjemahan menggunakan gettext PO) (``mo``)"

#: user/files.rst:36
msgid "CSV (``csv``)"
msgstr "CSV (``csv``)"

#: user/files.rst:37
msgid "Excel Open XML (``xlsx``)"
msgstr "Excel Open XML (``xlsx``)"

#: user/files.rst:38
msgid "JSON (only available for monolingual translations) (``json``)"
msgstr "JSON (hanya tersedia untuk terjemahan ekabahasa) (``json``)"

#: user/files.rst:39
msgid ""
"JSON nested structure file (only available for monolingual translations) "
"(``json-nested``)"
msgstr ""
"Berkas struktur bersarang JSON (hanya tersedia untuk terjemahan ekabahasa) "
"(``json-nested``)"

#: user/files.rst:40
msgid ""
"Android String Resource (only available for monolingual translations) "
"(``aresource``)"
msgstr ""
"Sumber Daya String Android (hanya tersedia untuk terjemahan ekabahasa) "
"(``aresource``)"

#: user/files.rst:41
msgid "iOS strings (only available for monolingual translations) (``strings``)"
msgstr "String iOS (hanya tersedia untuk terjemahan ekabahasa) (``strings``)"

#: user/files.rst:45
msgid ""
"The content available in the converted files differs based on file format "
"features, you can find overview in :ref:`fmt_capabs`."
msgstr ""
"Konten yang tersedia dalam berkas yang dikonversi berbeda berdasarkan fitur "
"format berkas, Anda dapat menemukan ikhtisarnya di :ref:`fmt_capabs`."

#: user/files.rst:52
msgid ""
":http:get:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"
msgstr ""
":http:get:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"

#: user/files.rst:58
msgid "Downloading components, categories or projects"
msgstr "Mengunduh komponen, kategori, atau proyek"

#: user/files.rst:60
msgid ""
"Translation files for a component, category or project can be downloaded at "
"once via the :guilabel:`Files` menu. The download is always served as a ZIP "
"file, and you can choose original or converted formats similarly as "
"in :ref:`download`."
msgstr ""
"Berkas terjemahan untuk suatu komponen, kategori, atau proyek dapat diunduh "
"langsung melalui menu :guilabel:`Berkas`. Unduhan selalu disajikan sebagai "
"berkas ZIP, dan Anda dapat memilih format asli atau yang telah dikonversi, "
"sama seperti pada :ref:`download`."

#: user/files.rst:67
msgid ":http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/file/`"
msgstr ":http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/file/`"

#: user/files.rst:72
msgid "Uploading translations"
msgstr "Mengunggah terjemahan"

#: user/files.rst:74
msgid ""
"When you have made your changes, use :guilabel:`Upload translation` in "
"the :guilabel:`Files` menu."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda membuat perubahan, gunakan :guilabel:`Unggah terjemahan` di "
"menu :guilabel:`Berkas`."

#: user/files.rst:82
msgid "Supported file formats"
msgstr "Format berkas yang didukung"

#: user/files.rst:84
msgid ""
"Any file in a supported file format can be uploaded, but it is still "
"recommended to use the same file format as the one used for translation, "
"otherwise some features might not be translated properly."
msgstr ""
"Berkas apa pun dalam format berkas yang didukung dapat diunggah, tetapi "
"tetap disarankan untuk menggunakan format berkas yang sama seperti yang "
"digunakan untuk terjemahan, jika tidak, beberapa fitur mungkin tidak "
"diterjemahkan dengan benar."

#: user/files.rst:96
msgid "Import methods"
msgstr "Metode impor"

#: user/files.rst:98
msgid "These are the choices presented when uploading translation files:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah pilihan yang ditampilkan saat mengunggah berkas terjemahan:"

#: user/files.rst:102
msgid "Add as translation (``translate``)"
msgstr "Tambahkan sebagai terjemahan (``translate``)"

#: user/files.rst:103
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as translations to existing strings. This is the "
"most common usecase, and the default behavior."
msgstr ""
"String yang diimpor ditambahkan sebagai terjemahan ke string yang sudah ada. "
"Ini adalah kasus penggunaan yang paling umum, dan merupakan perilaku bawaan."

#: user/files.rst:106 user/files.rst:113 user/files.rst:120 user/files.rst:127
msgid ""
"Only translations are used from the uploaded file and no additional content."
msgstr ""
"Hanya terjemahan yang digunakan dari berkas yang diunggah dan tidak ada "
"konten tambahan."

#: user/files.rst:108 user/files.rst:129
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Edit strings\" "
"permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"Pilihan ini hanya tersedia jika pengguna memiliki :ref:`izin \"Sunting "
"string\" <privileges>`."

#: user/files.rst:109
msgid "Add as suggestion (``suggest``)"
msgstr "Tambahkan sebagai saran (``suggest``)"

#: user/files.rst:110
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as suggestions. Do this when you want to have "
"your uploaded strings reviewed."
msgstr ""
"String yang diimpor ditambahkan sebagai saran. Lakukan ini ketika Anda ingin "
"string yang diunggah ditinjau."

#: user/files.rst:115
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Add suggestion\" "
"permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"Pilihan ini hanya tersedia jika pengguna memiliki :ref:`izin \"Tambahkan "
"saran\" <privileges>`."

#: user/files.rst:116
msgid "Add as approved translation (``approve``)"
msgstr "Tambahkan sebagai terjemahan yang disetujui (``approve``)"

#: user/files.rst:117
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as approved translations. Do this when you "
"already reviewed your translations before uploading them."
msgstr ""
"String yang diimpor akan ditambahkan sebagai terjemahan yang disetujui. "
"Lakukan ini ketika Anda telah meninjau terjemahan sebelum mengunggahnya."

#: user/files.rst:122
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Review strings\" "
"permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini hanya tersedia jika pengguna memiliki :ref:`izin \"Tinjau string\" "
"<privileges>`."

#: user/files.rst:123
msgid "Add as translation needing edit (``fuzzy``)"
msgstr "Tambahkan sebagai terjemahan yang perlu disunting (``fuzzy``)"

#: user/files.rst:124
msgid ""
"Imported strings are added as translations needing edit. This can be useful "
"when you want translations to be used, but also reviewed."
msgstr ""
"String yang diimpor ditambahkan sebagai terjemahan perlu disunting. Ini "
"berguna ketika Anda ingin terjemahan tersebut digunakan, tetapi juga perlu "
"ditinjau."

#: user/files.rst:130
msgid "Replace existing translation file (``replace``)"
msgstr "Ganti berkas terjemahan yang ada (``replace``)"

#: user/files.rst:131
msgid ""
"Existing file is replaced with new content. This can lead to loss of "
"existing translations, use with caution."
msgstr ""
"Berkas yang ada akan diganti dengan konten baru. Hal ini dapat menyebabkan "
"hilangnya terjemahan yang ada, jadi gunakan dengan hati-hati."

#: user/files.rst:134
msgid ""
"This option is available only if the user has the :ref:`\"Edit component "
"settings\" permission or \"Add new string\", \"Remove a string\" and \"Edit "
"strings\" permissions <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini hanya tersedia jika pengguna memiliki :ref:`izin \"Sunting "
"pengaturan komponen\" atau izin \"Tambahkan string baru\", \"Hapus string\" "
"and \"Sunting string\" <privileges>`."

#: user/files.rst:136
msgid "Update source strings (``source``)"
msgstr "Perbarui string sumber (``source``)"

#: user/files.rst:137
msgid ""
"Updates source strings in bilingual translation file. This is similar to "
"what :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.msgmerge` does."
msgstr ""
"Memperbarui string sumber dalam berkas terjemahan dwibahasa. Ini mirip "
"dengan yang dilakukan oleh :ref:`addon-weblate.gettext.msgmerge`."

#: user/files.rst:140
msgid ""
"This option is available only for some file formats and only if the user has "
"the :ref:`\"Upload translations\" permission <privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"Pilihan ini hanya tersedia untuk beberapa format berkas dan hanya jika "
"pengguna memiliki :ref:`izin \"Unggah terjemahan\" <privileges>`."

#: user/files.rst:142
msgid "Add new strings (``add``)"
msgstr "Tambahkan string baru (``add``)"

#: user/files.rst:143
msgid ""
"Adds new strings to the translation. It skips the ones which already exist."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan string baru ke terjemahan. String yang sudah ada akan dilewati."

#: user/files.rst:145
msgid ""
"In case you want to both add new strings and update existing translations, "
"upload the file second time with :guilabel:`Add as translation`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin menambahkan string baru dan memperbarui terjemahan yang ada, "
"unggah berkas untuk kedua kalinya dengan :guilabel:`Tambahkan sebagai "
"terjemahan`."

#: user/files.rst:148
msgid ""
"Only source, translation and key (context) are used from the uploaded file."
msgstr ""
"Hanya sumber, terjemahan, dan kunci (konteks) yang digunakan dari berkas "
"yang diunggah."

#: user/files.rst:150
msgid ""
"This option is available only with :ref:`component-manage_units` turned on "
"and only if the user has the :ref:`\"Add new string\" permission "
"<privileges>`."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini hanya tersedia jika :ref:`component-manage_units` dinyalakan dan "
"hanya jika pengguna memiliki :ref:`izin \"Tambahkan string baru\" "
"<privileges>`."

#: user/files.rst:155
msgid ""
":http:post:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"
msgstr ""
":http:post:`/api/translations/(string:project)/(string:component)/"
"(string:language)/file/`"

#: user/files.rst:160
msgid "Conflicts handling"
msgstr "Penanganan konflik"

#: user/files.rst:162
msgid "Defines how to deal with uploaded strings which are already translated:"
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan cara menangani string yang diunggah yang sudah diterjemahkan:"

#: user/files.rst:164
msgid "Change only untranslated strings (``ignore``)"
msgstr "Ubah hanya string yang tidak diterjemahkan (``ignore``)"

#: user/files.rst:165
msgid "Ignore uploaded translations which are already translated."
msgstr "Abaikan terjemahan yang diunggah yang sudah diterjemahkan."

#: user/files.rst:166
msgid "Change translated strings (``replace-translated``)"
msgstr "Ubah string yang diterjemahkan (``replace-translated``)"

#: user/files.rst:167
msgid ""
"Replace existing translations with uploaded ones, but keep approved ones."
msgstr ""
"Ganti terjemahan yang ada dengan terjemahan yang diunggah, tetapi "
"pertahankan terjemahan yang disetujui."

#: user/files.rst:168
msgid "Change translated and approved strings (``replace-approved``)"
msgstr "Ubah string yang diterjemahkan dan disetujui (``replace-approved``)"

#: user/files.rst:169
msgid ""
"Replace existing translations with uploaded ones, including approved ones."
msgstr ""
"Ganti terjemahan yang ada dengan terjemahan yang diunggah, termasuk yang "
"disetujui."

#: user/files.rst:174
msgid "Strings needing edit"
msgstr "String yang perlu disunting"

#: user/files.rst:176
msgid ""
"There is also an option for how to handle strings needing edit in the "
"imported file. Such strings can be handle in one of the three following "
"ways: \"Do not import\", \"Import as string needing edit\", or \"Import as "
"translated\"."
msgstr ""
"Terdapat juga opsi untuk menangani string yang perlu disunting dalam berkas "
"yang diimpor. String tersebut dapat ditangani dengan salah satu dari tiga "
"cara berikut: \"Jangan impor\", \"Impor sebagai string yang perlu "
"disunting\", atau \"Impor sebagai terjemahan\"."

#: user/files.rst:184
msgid "Overriding authorship"
msgstr "Menimpakan kepengarangan"

#: user/files.rst:186
msgid ""
"With admin permissions, you can also specify authorship of uploaded file. "
"This can be useful in case you've received the file in another way and want "
"to merge it into existing translations while properly crediting the actual "
"author."
msgstr ""
"Dengan izin admin, Anda juga dapat menspesifikasikan kepengarangan berkas "
"yang diunggah. Ini berguna jika Anda menerima berkas tersebut dengan cara "
"lain dan ingin menggabungkannya ke dalam terjemahan yang sudah ada, "
"sekaligus mencantumkan nama penulis aslinya dengan benar."

#: user/glossary.rst:6
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Each project can include one or more glossaries as a shorthand for "
#| "storing terminology. Glossaries help to maintain consistency of the "
#| "translation."
msgid ""
"Each project can include one or more glossaries for storing terms and their "
"preferred translations. Glossaries help keep translations consistent by "
"showing matching terms in the translation editor."
msgstr ""
"Setiap proyek dapat menyertakan satu atau lebih glosarium sebagai singkatan "
"untuk menyimpan terminologi. Glosarium membantu menjaga konsistensi "
"terjemahan."

#: user/glossary.rst:10
msgid ""
"Glossaries are regular translation components with special behavior. The "
"source language stores the terms Weblate searches for in source strings. "
"Each glossary translation stores the preferred term, forbidden term, or "
"untranslatable entry for one target language."
msgstr ""

#: user/glossary.rst:15
msgid ""
"Terms from the glossary containing words from the currently translated "
"source string are displayed in the sidebar of the translation editor."
msgstr ""

#: user/glossary.rst:20
msgid ""
"The glossary terms are not used in quality checks unless you enable that, "
"see :ref:`check-check-glossary` for more information."
msgstr ""
"Istilah glosarium tidak digunakan dalam pemeriksaan kualitas kecuali Anda "
"mengaktifkannya, lihat :ref:`check-check-glossary` untuk informasi lebih "
"lanjut."

#: user/glossary.rst:24
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Improved glossary matching."
msgid "How glossary matching works"
msgstr "Meningkatkan pencocokan glosarium."

#: user/glossary.rst:26
msgid ""
"When you translate a regular component, Weblate searches the source string "
"for terms from the source language of the project glossaries. When a term "
"matches, Weblate looks up the corresponding glossary entry for the language "
"currently being translated and shows it in the editor."
msgstr ""

#: user/glossary.rst:31
msgid ""
"This means glossary entries need to exist in the target glossary language to "
"be shown while translating that target language. A source-language-only "
"glossary can still store definitions and context, but it will not provide "
"target-language matches for languages that do not have glossary entries."
msgstr ""

#: user/glossary.rst:36
msgid ""
"If you want a term to be present in every glossary language, mark the source "
"entry as :ref:`glossary-terminology`. If the term should stay unchanged in "
"every language, use :ref:`glossary-untranslatable`; combine it with "
"terminology only when you want Weblate to create and maintain entries for "
"all glossary languages."
msgstr ""

#: user/glossary.rst:42
msgid "Managing glossaries"
msgstr "Mengelola glosarium"

#: user/glossary.rst:46
msgid ""
"Glossaries are now regular translation components and you can use all "
"Weblate features on them — commenting, storing in a remote repository, or "
"adding explanations."
msgstr ""
"Glosarium sekarang menjadi komponen terjemahan reguler dan Anda dapat "
"menggunakan semua fitur Weblate di dalamnya — memberikan komentar, menyimpan "
"dalam repositori jarak jauh, atau menambahkan penjelasan."

#: user/glossary.rst:50
msgid ""
"Use any component as a glossary by turning on :ref:`component-is_glossary`. "
"You can create multiple glossaries for one project."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan komponen apa pun sebagai glosarium dengan menyalakan :ref:`component-"
"is_glossary`. Anda dapat membuat beberapa glosarium untuk satu proyek."

#: user/glossary.rst:53
msgid ""
"An empty glossary for a given project is automatically created with the "
"project. Glossaries are shared among all components of the same project, and "
"optionally with other projects using :ref:`component-links` from the "
"respective glossary component."
msgstr ""
"Glosarium kosong untuk proyek tertentu akan otomatis dibuat bersama proyek "
"tersebut. Glosarium dibagikan di antara semua komponen dalam proyek yang "
"sama, dan secara opsional dengan proyek lain menggunakan :ref:`component-"
"links` dari komponen glosarium masing-masing."

#: user/glossary.rst:58
msgid ""
"The glossary component looks like any other component in Weblate with added "
"colored label:"
msgstr ""
"Komponen glosarium tampak seperti komponen lain di Weblate dengan tambahan "
"label berwarna:"

#: user/glossary.rst:63
msgid "You can browse all glossary terms:"
msgstr "Anda dapat menelusuri semua istilah di glosarium:"

#: user/glossary.rst:67
msgid "or edit them as any translations."
msgstr "atau menyuntingnya sebagai terjemahan apa pun."

#: user/glossary.rst:70
msgid "Glossary terms"
msgstr "Istilah glosarium"

#: user/glossary.rst:72
msgid ""
"Glossary terms are translated the same way regular strings are. You can "
"toggle additional features using the :guilabel:`Tools` menu for each term."
msgstr ""
"Istilah glosarium diterjemahkan dengan cara yang sama seperti string "
"reguler. Anda dapat mengubah fitur tambahan menggunakan "
"menu :guilabel:`Alat` untuk setiap istilah."

