msgid ""
"Screenshots can be uploaded directly from this panel using :guilabel:`Add "
"screenshot`, or managed elsewhere in Weblate to better inform translators of "
"where and how the string is used. Source-language screenshots are shown for "
"every translation of the string, while translation-specific screenshots are "
"shown only for that translation; see :ref:`screenshots`."
msgstr ""

#: user/translating.rst:384
msgid "Nearby strings"
msgstr "String terdekat"

#: user/translating.rst:385
msgid ""
"Displays neighbouring strings from the translation file. These are usually "
"also used in a similar context and prove useful in keeping the translation "
"consistent."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan string yang berdekatan dari berkas terjemahan. String ini "
"biasanya juga digunakan dalam konteks yang serupa dan terbukti bermanfaat "
"dalam menjaga konsistensi terjemahan."

#: user/translating.rst:388
msgid "Other occurrences"
msgstr "Kemunculan lain"

#: user/translating.rst:389
msgid ""
"In case a message appears in multiple places (e.g. multiple components), "
"this tab shows all of them if they are found to be inconsistent "
"(see :ref:`check-inconsistent`). You can choose which one to use."
msgstr ""
"Jika sebuah pesan muncul di beberapa tempat (misalnya beberapa komponen), "
"tab ini akan menampilkan semuanya jika ditemukan tidak konsisten "
"(lihat :ref:`check-inconsistent`). Anda dapat memilih salah satu yang akan "
"digunakan."

#: user/translating.rst:393
msgid "Look at similar strings translated in past, see :ref:`memory`."
msgstr ""
"Lihat string serupa yang diterjemahkan di masa lalu, lihat :ref:`memory`."

#: user/translating.rst:395
msgid "Displays terms from the project glossary used in the current message."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan istilah dari glosarium proyek yang digunakan dalam pesan saat "
"ini."

#: user/translating.rst:396
msgid "History"
msgstr "Riwayat"

#: user/translating.rst:397
msgid "List of people whom have changed this message recently using Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Daftar orang yang baru-baru ini mengubah pesan ini menggunakan Weblate."

#: user/translating.rst:398
msgid "Project"
msgstr "Proyek"

#: user/translating.rst:399
msgid ""
"Project info like instructions for translators, or a directory or link to "
"the string in the version control system repository the project uses."
msgstr ""
"Info proyek seperti petunjuk untuk penerjemah, atau direktori atau tautan ke "
"string dalam repositori sistem kontrol versi yang digunakan proyek."

#: user/translating.rst:402
msgid "If you want direct links, the translation format has to support it."
msgstr "Jika Anda ingin tautan langsung, format terjemahan harus mendukungnya."

#: user/translating.rst:405
msgid "Translation history"
msgstr "Riwayat terjemahan"

#: user/translating.rst:407
msgid ""
"Every change is by default (unless turned-off in component settings) saved "
"in the database, and can be reverted. Optionally, translations can also be "
"reverted in the underlying version control system."
msgstr ""
"Setiap perubahan secara bawaan (kecuali dimatikan dalam pengaturan komponen) "
"tersimpan dalam basis data, dan dapat dikembalikan. Secara opsional, "
"terjemahan juga dapat dikembalikan dalam sistem kontrol versi yang "
"mendasarinya."

#: user/translating.rst:413
msgid "Translated string length"
msgstr "Panjang string yang diterjemahkan"

#: user/translating.rst:415
msgid ""
"Weblate can limit the length of a translation in several ways to ensure the "
"translated string is not too long:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate dapat membatasi panjang terjemahan dalam beberapa cara untuk "
"memastikan string yang diterjemahkan tidak terlalu panjang:"

#: user/translating.rst:418
msgid ""
"The default limitation for translation is ten times longer than the source "
"string. This can be modified "
"with :setting:`LIMIT_TRANSLATION_LENGTH_BY_SOURCE_LENGTH`. If you are "
"hitting this, it can also be caused by a monolingual translation being "
"wrongly set up as a bilingual one, making Weblate mistaking the translation "
"key for the actual source string. See :ref:`bimono` for more info."
msgstr ""
"Batasan bawaan untuk terjemahan adalah sepuluh kali lebih panjang daripada "
"string sumber. Batasan ini dapat diubah "
"dengan :setting:`LIMIT_TRANSLATION_LENGTH_BY_SOURCE_LENGTH`. Jika Anda "
"mengalami hal ini, hal ini juga dapat disebabkan oleh terjemahan ekabahasa "
"yang salah diatur sebagai terjemahan dwibahasa, sehingga Weblate salah "
"memasukkan kunci terjemahan ke string sumber yang sebenarnya. "
"Lihat :ref:`bimono` untuk info lebih lanjut."

#: user/translating.rst:423
msgid ""
"Maximum length in characters defined by the translation file or flag, as "
"per :ref:`check-max-length`."
msgstr ""
"Panjang maksimum dalam karakter didefinisikan oleh berkas terjemahan atau "
"penanda, sesuai :ref:`check-max-length`."

#: user/translating.rst:425
msgid ""
"Maximal rendered size in pixels as defined by flags; see :ref:`check-max-"
"size`."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran render maksimal dalam piksel seperti yang didefinisikan oleh penanda; "
"lihat :ref:`check-max-size`."

#: user/translating.rst:432
msgid ""
"Based on configuration and your translated language, Weblate provides "
"suggestions from several machine translation tools and :ref:`translation-"
"memory`. All machine translations are available in a single tab of each "
"translation page."
msgstr ""
"Berdasarkan konfigurasi dan bahasa terjemahan Anda, Weblate menyediakan "
"saran dari beberapa alat terjemahan mesin dan :ref:`translation-memory`. "
"Semua terjemahan mesin tersedia dalam satu tab di setiap halaman terjemahan."

#: user/translating.rst:436
msgid ""
"You can also perform a concordance search on the :ref:`translation-memory`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat melakukan pencarian konkordansi pada :ref:`translation-"
"memory`."

#: user/translating.rst:440
msgid ""
"You can find the list of supported tools in :ref:`machine-translation-setup`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menemukan daftar alat yang didukung di :ref:`machine-translation-"
"setup`."

#: user/translating.rst:447
msgid ""
"You can use automatic translation to bootstrap translation based on external "
"sources. This tool is called :guilabel:`Automatic translation` accessible in "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` menu, once you have selected a component and a "
"language:"
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menggunakan terjemahan otomatis untuk memulai terjemahan "
"berdasarkan sumber eksternal. Alat ini disebut :guilabel:`Terjemahan "
"otomatis` yang dapat diakses di menu :guilabel:`Operasi`, setelah Anda "
"memilih komponen dan bahasa:"

#: user/translating.rst:453
msgid ""
"A similar operation :guilabel:`Batch automatic translation` is available if "
"you have selected a project language, a component or a category."
msgstr ""
"Operasi serupa :guilabel:`Terjemahan otomatis batch` tersedia jika Anda "
"memilih bahasa proyek, komponen, atau kategori."

#: user/translating.rst:456
msgid "Two modes of operation are possible:"
msgstr "Ada dua mode operasi yang mungkin:"

#: user/translating.rst:458
msgid "Using other Weblate components as a source for translations."
msgstr "Menggunakan komponen Weblate lainnya sebagai sumber terjemahan."

#: user/translating.rst:459
msgid ""
"Using selected machine translation services with translations above a "
"certain quality threshold."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan layanan terjemahan mesin terpilih dengan terjemahan di atas "
"ambang batas kualitas tertentu."

#: user/translating.rst:462
msgid ""
"When using other components as the source, Weblate applies translations only "
"when plural forms are compatible. If the source component uses different "
"plural rules, pluralized strings are skipped and Weblate shows a warning, "
"while single-form strings are still translated."
msgstr ""

#: user/translating.rst:467
msgid "You can also choose which strings are to be auto-translated."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat memilih string mana yang akan diterjemahkan secara otomatis."

#: user/translating.rst:471
msgid ""
"Be mindful that this will overwrite existing translations if employed with "
"wide filters such as :guilabel:`All strings`."
msgstr ""
"Berhati-hatilah bahwa ini akan menimpa terjemahan yang ada jika digunakan "
"dengan filter lebar seperti :guilabel:`Semua string`."

#: user/translating.rst:474
msgid ""
"Useful in several situations like consolidating translation between "
"different components (for example the application and its website) or when "
"bootstrapping a translation for a new component using existing translations "
"(translation memory)."
msgstr ""
"Berguna dalam beberapa situasi seperti menggabungkan terjemahan antara "
"berbagai komponen (misalnya aplikasi dan situs webnya) atau saat melakukan "
"bootstrapping terjemahan untuk komponen baru menggunakan terjemahan yang ada "
"(memori terjemahan)."

#: user/translating.rst:479
msgid ""
"The automatically translated strings are labelled :guilabel:`Automatically "
"translated`."
msgstr ""
"String yang diterjemahkan secara otomatis diberi "
"label :guilabel:`Diterjemahkan secara otomatis`."

#: user/translating.rst:491
msgid ""
"To avoid abuse of the interface, rate limiting is applied to several "
"operations like searching, sending contact forms, or translating. If "
"affected by it, you are blocked for a certain period, until you can perform "
"the operation again."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghindari penyalahgunaan antarmuka, pembatasan akses diterapkan pada "
"beberapa operasi seperti pencarian, pengiriman formulir kontak, atau "
"terjemahan. Jika terpengaruh oleh pembatasan ini, Anda akan diblokir untuk "
"jangka waktu tertentu hingga Anda dapat melakukan operasi tersebut kembali."

#: user/translating.rst:496
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Default limits and fine-tuning is described in the administrative manual, "
#| "see :ref:`rate-limit`."
msgid ""
"Default limits and fine-tuning are described in the administrative manual, "
"see :ref:`rate-limit`."
msgstr ""
"Batasan bawaan dan penyempurnaan dijelaskan dalam manual administratif, "
"lihat :ref:`rate-limit`."

#: user/translating.rst:502
msgid "Search and replace"
msgstr "Cari dan ganti"

#: user/translating.rst:504
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Change terminology effectively or perform bulk fixing of the strings "
#| "using :guilabel:`Search and replace` in the :guilabel:`Tools` menu."
