msgstr ""
"Ubah terminologi secara efektif atau lakukan perbaikan massal string "
"menggunakan :guilabel:`Cari dan ganti` di menu :guilabel:`Alat`."

#: user/translating.rst:511
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Don't worry about messing up the strings, as it is a two-step process. A "
