#: user/translating.rst:543
msgid "Matrix View"
msgstr "Tampilan Matriks"

#: user/translating.rst:545
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You can compare different languages efficiently using this view. It is "
#| "available on every component page, from the :guilabel:`Tools` menu. First "
#| "select all languages you want to compare, confirm your selection, then "
#| "click on any translation to open and edit it."
msgid ""
"You can compare different languages efficiently using this view. It is "
"available on every component page, from the :guilabel:`Operations` menu. "
"First select all languages you want to compare, confirm your selection, then "
"click on any translation to open and edit it."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membandingkan berbagai bahasa secara efisien menggunakan tampilan "
"ini. Tampilan ini tersedia di setiap halaman komponen, dari "
"menu :guilabel:`Alat`. Pertama, pilih semua bahasa yang ingin Anda "
"bandingkan, konfirmasikan pilihan Anda, lalu klik terjemahan mana pun untuk "
"membuka dan menyuntingnya."

#: user/translating.rst:550
msgid ""
"The matrix view is also a very good starting point to find missing "
"translations in different languages, and quickly add them from one view."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan matriks juga merupakan titik awal yang sangat baik untuk menemukan "
"terjemahan yang hilang dalam berbagai bahasa, dan dengan cepat "
"menambahkannya dari satu tampilan."

#: user/translating.rst:558
msgid "Zen Mode"
msgstr "Mode Zen"

#: user/translating.rst:559
msgid ""
"This mode simplifies the layout and removes additional UI elements such "
"as :guilabel:`Nearby strings` or the :guilabel:`Glossary`. It is available "
"by clicking the :guilabel:`Zen` button on the top-right of the regular "
"editor (translation of a string)."
msgstr ""
"Mode ini menyederhanakan tata letak dan menghapus elemen UI tambahan "
"seperti :guilabel:`String terdekat` atau :guilabel:`Glosarium`. Mode ini "
"tersedia dengan mengeklik tombol :guilabel:`Zen` di kanan atas penyunting "
"reguler (terjemahan string)."

#: user/translating.rst:564
msgid ""
"You can select the Zen editor as your default editor using the :ref:`profile-"
"preferences` tab on your :ref:`user-profile`. You can also choose there "
"between having translations listed :guilabel:`Top to bottom` "
"or :guilabel:`Side by side`, depending on your personal preference."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memilih penyunting Zen sebagai penyunting bawaan menggunakan "
"tab :ref:`profile-preferences` di :ref:`user-profile` Anda. Anda juga dapat "
"memilih antara menampilkan terjemahan dari :guilabel:`Atas ke bawah` atau "
"dari :guilabel:`Bersebelahan`, tergantung preferensi pribadi Anda."

