#: vcs.rst:83
msgid ""
"For self-hosted Weblate, a single private repository is often easiest to set "
"up using an HTTPS repository URL with an access token, see :doc:`/admin/code-"
"hosting`."
msgstr ""

#: vcs.rst:87
